msgid "HSV/HSL Formats"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../userspace-api/media/v4l/subdev-formats.rst:8661
msgid ""
"Those formats transfer pixel data as RGB values in a cylindrical-coordinate "
"system using Hue-Saturation-Value or Hue-Saturation-Lightness components. "
"The format code is made of the following information."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../userspace-api/media/v4l/subdev-formats.rst:8666
msgid ""
"The hue, saturation, value or lightness and optional alpha components order "
"code, as encoded in a pixel sample. The only currently supported value is "
"AHSV."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../userspace-api/media/v4l/subdev-formats.rst:8670
msgid ""
"The number of bits per component, for each component. The values can be "
"different for all components. The only currently supported value is 8888."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../userspace-api/media/v4l/subdev-formats.rst:8674
msgid ""
"The number of bus samples per pixel. Pixels that are wider than the bus "
"width must be transferred in multiple samples. The only currently supported "
"value is 1."
msgstr ""

